label: Case Density
definition: Number of cases per 100k population calculated using a 7-day rolling average

label: Test Positivity Ratio
definition: Ratio of people who test positive calculated using a 7-day rolling average

label: Weekly COVID Admissions per 100K population
definition: Number of COVID patients per 100k population admitted in the past week

label: Vaccinations Completed Ratio
definition: Ratio of population that has completed vaccinations

label: Deaths
definition: Cumulative deaths that are suspected or confirmed to have been caused by COVID-19.
